    {
      "Id": "1CAE61F1-4A53-411C-9806-76F23EC9981B",
      "OrderNumber": 2,
      "ExternalTitle": "Online Payments Portal",
      "ExternalUrl": "/#/departlist;id=8AAF6B9B-864F-43CA-917F-EFBE30108654",
      "Title": "Online Payments Portal",
      "Description": "<hr />\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">The <strong>CUK&nbsp;Online Payments Portal</strong> is a centralized online payment solution which can be used by&nbsp;<strong>Students/Candidates, Job Aspirants, Suppliers, etc</strong>. for online payments towards Central Univesity of Kashmir. Use the following instructions to make the payments using the portal:</p>\n<ol style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<ol style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Click on the CUK&nbsp;Online Payments Portal Link to visit the portal</li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Select the Payment type (e.g: Admission Fee, Recruitment Fee, Hostel Fee, etc.) from the Dropdown and click&nbsp;<u>Continue</u></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Fill the required form fields.&nbsp;<strong>Check/Verify</strong> the Total Fee generated and Click on&nbsp;<u>Submit</u></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">The System will generate the Unique Payment Id. Click on&nbsp;<u>Make Payment</u></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">On the Next screen, the details entered, including the amount of payment is displayed. Again verfiy the amount and click on&nbsp;<u>proceed to make payment.</u></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">The Payment can be made using&nbsp;<strong>Debit Card/Credit Card or Net Banking</strong>. Use your preffered option to complete the Payment process.</li>\n</ol>\n</ol>\n<ol style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\">Take the print out of the Payment receipt generated for your reference.</li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">For any Queries related to online payment, contact Mr Aijaz Habib (9541178773)</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif; font-size: medium; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: #ffffff; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: center;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: none; background: none 0% 0% repeat scroll #007fff; display: inline-block; text-align: center; padding: 10px; border-radius: 5px;\" href=\"https://www.eduqfix.com/cuk/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"color: #ffffff;\"><strong>CUK Online Payments Portal</strong></span></a></p>",
